   "source": [
    "# Texture Viewer/Reader"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# this file only exists in the base version of the game. it even has transparency\n",
    "# bonus: I'm a corpo shill, so...\n",
    "sample_texture = r\"art\\texture_library\\decal\\diffuse\\sarif_logo_b_d_diffuse.drm\"\n",
    "\n",
    "from pyDXHR.cdcEngine.Archive import Archive\n",
    "from pyDXHR.cdcEngine.DRM.DRMFile import DRM\n",
    "from pyDXHR.cdcEngine.DRM.SectionTypes import SectionType\n",
    "from pyDXHR.cdcEngine.Sections.RenderResource import RenderResource"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def display_render_resource_to_jupyter(rr):\n",
    "    \"\"\" Helper function to display a RenderResource object to a jupyter notebook. PIL can handle DDS images, so the only conversion is done from PCD/PS3T to DDS\"\"\"\n",
    "    from PIL import Image\n",
    "    import io\n",
    "    \n",
    "    image_data = rr.Image.write_as()\n",
    "\n",
    "    image = Image.open(io.BytesIO(image_data))\n",
    "    display(image)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.DdsImagePlugin.DdsImageFile image mode=RGBA size=512x512>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pc_base = Archive()\n",
    "pc_base.deserialize_from_file(r\"..........\\PC_BASE\\BIGFILE.000\")\n",
    "\n",
    "pc_base_raw_data = pc_base.get_from_filename(sample_texture)\n",
    "pc_base_drm = DRM()\n",
    "pc_base_drm.deserialize(pc_base_raw_data)\n",
    "\n",
    "pc_tex_sec = pc_base_drm.filter_by_type([SectionType.RenderResource])[0]\n",
    "pc_rr = RenderResource(section=pc_tex_sec)\n",
    "display_render_resource_to_jupyter(pc_rr)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.DdsImagePlugin.DdsImageFile image mode=RGBA size=512x512>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "ps3_base_cache = Archive() \n",
    "ps3_base_cache.deserialize_from_file(r\"........\\PS3_BASE\\CACHE.000\")\n",
    "\n",
    "ps3_base_raw_data = ps3_base_cache.get_from_filename(sample_texture)\n",
    "ps3_base_drm = DRM()\n",
    "ps3_base_drm.deserialize(ps3_base_raw_data)\n",
    "\n",
    "ps3_tex_sec = ps3_base_drm.filter_by_type([SectionType.RenderResource])[0]\n",
    "ps3_rr = RenderResource(section=ps3_tex_sec)\n",
    "display_render_resource_to_jupyter(ps3_rr)"
   ]
  }
 ],
